snippet.title: Johnny Depp Let Go from Warner Brothers Movie After Losing Case with the Sun Involving Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp's life is kind of mess right now. He was involved in a case in the UK regarding an article they wrote about him which he claimed was false. A judge ruled that the Sun did nothing wrong. Now Warner Brothers let him go.
